---
title: Honey-Glazed Haloumi Bowl with Roasted Cauliflower & Israeli Couscous
description: There was complete mayhem when this dish hit our tasting table. With sweet honey on warm, salty haloumi, plus chermoula-spiced veggies and a cooling yoghurt, it disappeared from the bowl in record time. Enjoy!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/honey-haloumi-roasted-cauliflower-bowl-6b10a107.jpg
